summary.span: 包含針對 HTTP 所定義的狀態碼值。

span.span: Contains the values of status codes defined for HTTP.

remarks.format: ## Remarks 列舉包含的 HTTP 1.1 RFC 2616 中所定義的狀態碼的值。The enumeration contains the values of the status codes defined in RFC 2616 for HTTP 1.1. HTTP 要求的狀態包含在屬性。The status of an HTTP request is contained in the property. 如果屬性是`false`，下列的列舉值會導致擲回例外狀況：If the property is `false`, the following enumeration values cause an exception to be thrown: - `Ambiguous` - `Found` - `MultipleChoices` - `Redirect` - `RedirectKeepVerb` - `RedirectMethod` - `SeeOther` - `TemporaryRedirect` ## Examples 下列範例會比較所傳回的狀態的成員類別，以判斷回應的狀態。The following example compares the status returned by an with a member of the class to determine the status of a response.
